<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_4c9aaec1-ba52-4646-8a33-d2bb85d957d5" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>J3D5</sptc><title id="_339f4f97-63ef-451d-b587-1bab719c6e2d">Roof thermal breaks of a Class 4 part of a building</title><archive-num/><subclause id="_e6081bdd-3a36-4bf8-b8ab-43851a4cac66" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_adf24463-e316-4da3-95d5-c0603232f615">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>A metal-framed flat, skillion or cathedral roof that—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_b4210a22-1394-424b-bec9-95efe8854d81">has metal sheet roofing directly fixed to metal purlins, metal rafters, metal battens or the like; and</li><li id="_c9f375c5-5d6b-47ee-b0d8-2c8dcb839002">does not have a ceiling lining or has a ceiling lining fixed directly to the metal purlins, metal rafters,  metal battens or the like; and</li><li id="_50f17ba0-068a-4116-b6f1-cc2d3eeffc84">has not achieved the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_be210e49-0a0b-4cf7-816d-c5fe64f5e55d" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">required </xref><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1490_25.4.0.xml#_bf26e61b-dbc1-4c09-b8be-ac8d936c0ac9" id="_fb1361ca-f73d-4aa1-b921-c59426787e73" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Total R-Value</xref> specified in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/6287_0.20.0.xml#_891ecf3d-816f-4cf1-aac4-7aac94e96209" id="_84343afa-4b66-4905-be26-1e595b40ff12" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">Table J3D7t</xref>, calculated using a method that accounts for the effects of thermal bridging,</li></ol><p>must have a thermal break, consisting of a material with an <xref xmlns:qxa="urn:schemas-quark-com:xmlauthor" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1420_0.4.0.xml#_f438bdfd-6adb-43c4-b342-7b1656af23c4" id="_41afd9e4-d177-47cc-99b4-bc237cfeb3b6" qxa:read-only="true" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="true" type="glossterm">R-Value</xref> of greater than or equal to R0.2, installed within the structure.</p></subclause><subclause id="_1f67b10b-47bd-4620-9b43-713851b8001c" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_ad799bf8-1cce-45e4-80f8-ac0ba514f9ab">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>The requirements of (1) do not apply to roofs constructed using insulated sandwich panels.</p></subclause></clause>